# рџ”№ 2. Maven Configuration

рџ“„ `pom.xml` (important parts)

```xml
<project xmlns="http://maven.apache.org/POM/4.0.0">
    <modelVersion>4.0.0</modelVersion>

    <groupId>com.ecommerce</groupId>
    <artifactId>order-system</artifactId>
    <version>1.0</version>

